sources.title: Liane Jungle Goddess 1956 202511
sources.description: Still another white jungle goddess movie this time with a young Marion Micheal in the lead role. Not a lot to say about plot or character development as these movies all are about the same.   There are sort of three of Liane movies, this one, Nature Girl and the Slaver, and Liane, die Tochter des Dschungels,  The last one only has Liane in archive footage.  This is the English version with a little less nudity.
